ed sectors. Participation in the Technical Committees is open to those institutions that have the interest, expertise and capacity to engage in and contribute to the work of the sector.</p>\n'),(757,209,'_wp_attached_file','2018/03/documents.png'),(758,209,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:200;s:6:\"height\";i:200;s:4:\"file\";s:21:\"2018/03/documents.png\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:2:{s:29:\"woocommerce_gallery_thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:21:\"documents-100x100.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:100;s:6:\"height\";i:100;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:9:\"image/png\";}s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:21:\"documents-150x150.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:150;s:6:\"height\";i:150;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:9:\"image/png\";}}s:10:\"image_meta\";a:12:{s:8:\"aperture\";s:1:\"0\";s:6:\"credit\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"camera\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"created_timestamp\";s:1:\"0\";s:9:\"copyright\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"focal_length\";s:1:\"0\";s:3:\"iso\";s:1:\"0\";s:13:\"shutter_speed\";s:1:\"0\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"orientation\";s:1:\"0\";s:8:\"keywords\";a:0:{}}}'),(759,210,'_wp_attached_file','2018/03/programs_corn.png'),(760,210,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:200;s:6:\"height\";i:200;s:4:\"file\";s:25:\"2018/03/programs_corn.png\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:2:{s:29:\"woocommerce_gallery_thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:25:\"programs_corn-100x100.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:100;s:6:\"height\";i:100;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:9:\"image/png\";}s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:25:\"programs_corn-150x150.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:150;s:6:\"height\";i:150;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:9:\"image/png\";}}s:10:\"image_meta\";a:12:{s:8:\"aperture\";s:1:\"0\";s:6:\"credit\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"camera\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"created_timestamp\";s:1:\"0\";s:9:\"copyright\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"focal_length\";s:1:\"0\";s:3:\"iso\";s:1:\"0\";s:13:\"shutter_speed\";s:1:\"0\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"orientation\";s:1:\"0\";s:8:\"keywords\";a:0:{}}}'),(761,211,'_wp_attached_file','2018/03/yellowpages.