 objective: Facilitate technical, operational and strategic level dialogue between the government and DPs and to mobilize and align development investments towards sector priorities identified by the GoE, as well as to harmonize investment and activities in order to maximize resource effectiveness.</p>\r\r\n\r\r\n							\r\r\n							\r\n\r\r\n							\r\r\n                            <a class=\"button theme-bg animated\" href=\"http://www.moa-redfs.gov.et/about-us/\">LEARN MORE</a>\r\r\n                        </div>\r\r\n                    </div>\r\r\n                </div>\r\r\n				\r\n			\r\r\n				\r\n				<div class=\"single-slider pb-340 pt-240 bg-img\" style=\"background-image:url(http://www.moa-redfs.gov.et/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/24520671422_a45ac55a90_b.jpg);\" data-overlay=\"5\">\r\r\n                    <div class=\"container\">\r\r\n                        <div class=\"slider-text text-center z-index\">\r\r\n                            <h2 class=\"animated\">Working Group <span></span></h2>\r\r\n                            <h1 class=\"animated\"> <span></span>  <span></span></h1>\r\r\n                            <p class=\"animated\">The joint platform brings togehter the Government of Ethiopia (GoE), represented by the federal  Ministry of Agriculture and Natural Resources (MoANR), Ministiry of Livestock and Fisheries (MoLF),  and the main development partners (DPs) engaged in the sectors.</p>\r\r\n\r\r\n							\r\r\n							\r\n\r\r\n							\r\r\n                            <a class=\"button theme-bg animated\" href=\"http://www.moa-redfs.gov.et/faqs\">LEARN MORE</a>\r\r\n                        </div>\r\r\n                    </div>\r\r\n                </div>\r\r\n				\r\n			\r\r\n				\r\n				<div class=\"single-slider pb-340 pt-240 bg-img\" style=\"background-image:url(http://www.moa-redfs.gov.et/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Ethiopian_woman_selling_crops_in_a_local_crowded_market-770x461.jpg);\" data-overlay=\"5\">\r\r\n                    <div class=\"container\">\r\r\n                        <div class=\"slider-text text-center z-index\">\r\r\n                            <h2 class=\"animated\">Technical Committees <span></span></h2>\r\r\n                            <h1 class=\"animated\"> <span></span>  <span></span></h1>\r\r\n                            <p class=\"animated\">Our technical committees are focused on the following: Livestock and Fisheries Production and Marketing; Agriculture Growth; Sustainable Land Management; and Rural Job Opportunity Creation and Food Security.</p>\r\r\n\r\r\n							\r\r\n							\r\n\r\r\n							\r\r\n                            <a class=\"button theme-bg animated\" href=\"http://www.moa-redfs.gov.et/yellow-pages/technical-committees/\">LEARN MORE</a>\r\r\n                        </div>\r\r\n                    </div>\r\r\n                </div>\r\r\n				\r\n				\r\r\n            </div>\r\r\n        </div>\r\r\n		<!-- Background Area End -->\r\r\n				\r\r\n	</div>\r\r\n	\r\r\n	</div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"kc-elm kc-css-2651967 kc_row\"><div class=\"kc-row-container  kc-container\"><div class=\"kc-wrap-columns\"><div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-1868119 kc_col-sm-12 kc_column kc_col-sm-12\"><div class=\"kc-col-container\"><div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-3884169 kc_row kc_row_inner all-single-service\"><div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-2809997 kc_col-sm-12 kc_column_inner kc_col-sm-12\"><div class=\"kc_wrapper kc-col-inner-container\">\r\n	<div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-1696513 \">\r\n		<div class=\"section-title text-center 370977 \">\r\n						<h2>About Us</h2>\r\n						<div class=\"icon-img\">\r\n				<img width=\"48\" height=\"36\" src=\"http://www.moa-redfs.gov.et/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/icon_hands_tiny.png\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"\" />			</div>\r\n						<p>The Rural Economic Development and Food Security (RED&amp;FS) Sector Working Group was established in 2008 with the purpose to act as a platform bringing together the Government of Ethiopia, with its Development Partners who are active in the Agriculture Sector. The broad objectives of the platform are to facilitate dialogue between the government and DPs, mobilize and direct development investments towards the identified priorities of the government, and harmonize those investments in order to enhance Resource Effectiveness.</p>\r\n					</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-1645001 kc_row kc_row_inner\"><div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-766056 kc_col-sm-3 kc_column_inner kc_col-sm-3\"><div class=\"kc_wrapper kc-col-inner-container\"><div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-812208 kc_shortcode kc_single_image\">\n\n        <img src=\"http://www.moa-redfs.gov.et/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/programs_corn.png\" class=\"\" alt=\"\" />    </div>\n\n<div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-4049644 kc-title-wrap \">\n\n	<h3 class=\"kc_title\">Programs</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-4204788 kc_text_block\"><p>Read more about the three flagship programs that RED&amp;FS supports.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-1697731\">\n	<a class=\"kc_button\" href=\"http://www.moa-redfs.gov.et/programs-2/\" target=\"_self\" title=\"\" onclick=\"\">\n		Read More	</a>\n</div>\n</div></div><div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-99247 kc_col-sm-3 kc_column_inner kc_col-sm-3\"><div class=\"kc_wrapper kc-col-inner-container\"><div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-3877231 kc_shortcode kc_single_image\">\n\n        <img src=\"http://www.moa-redfs.gov.et/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/documents.png\" class=\"\" alt=\"\" />    </div>\n\n<div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-514995 kc-title-wrap \">\n\n	<h3 class=\"kc_title\">Documents</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-771026 kc_text_block\"><p>Visit our document library which houses policy and technical documents, as well as information from committees.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-4215642\">\n	<a class=\"kc_button\" href=\"http://www.moa-redfs.gov.et/mdocuments-library/\" target=\"_self\" title=\"\" onclick=\"\">\n		See Documents	</a>\n</div>\n</div></div><div class=