ent and DPs and to mobilize and align development investments towards sector priorities identified by the GoE, as well as to harmonize investment and activities in order to maximize resource effectiveness. RED&amp;FS operates within the tenets and framework of the Paris Declaration on Aid Effectiveness.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\n<div class=\"grow-img\">\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium\" src=\"http://www.moa-redfs.gov.et/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/AboutUs_img1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"720\" height=\"544\" />\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- humanity & Client Section End -->\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section><section class=\"kc-elm kc-css-669716 kc_row#\">\r\n<div class=\"kc-row-container kc-container\">\r\n<div class=\"kc-wrap-columns\">\r\n<div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-773063 kc_col-sm-12 kc_column# kc_col-sm-12\">\r\n<div class=\"kc-col-container\">\r\n<div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-197423 \">\r\n<div class=\"section-title section-2 text-center \">\r\n<h2>RED&amp;FS Organizational Structure</h2>\r\nRED&amp;FS is built on four pillar Technical Committees (TCs) that mirror the state ministerial structure of the two federal ministries, each chaired by the respective sector state minister and supported by two DP co-chairs. The TCs are: Livestock and Fisheries Production and Marketing; Agriculture Growth; Sustainable Land Management; and Rural Job Opportunity Creation and Food Security. Each TC is further broken down into focused sub-sector Task Forces (TFs) which are chaired by a government director and co-chaired by DP representatives. Oversight to the entire structure is provided through an Executive Committee chaired by the two federal ministers and also supported by DP co-chairs. The platform also features cross-sector TFs not aligned to any specific sector. The RED&amp;FS Secretariat provides broad and agile support to the entire sector and consists of a Government Coordinator, Donor Coordinator, Monitoring and Evaluation (M&amp;E) Expert, and support staff. The RED&amp;FS Organizational Chart is shown below.\r\n<div class=\"icon-img-2\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium\" src=\"http://www.moa-redfs.gov.et/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/National-Agricultural-Investment-Framework.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"949\" height=\"695\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-804694 kc_row# kc_row#_inner\">\r\n<div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-413270 kc_col-sm-12 kc_column_inner kc_col-sm-12\">\r\n<div class=\"kc_wrapper kc-col-inner-container\">\r\n\r\n<!-- portfolio-area-start -->\r\n<div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-60286\"><section id=\"tf-portfolio-area\" class=\"tf-portfolio-wrap bg-white ptb-100 xtb-60\">\r\n<div class=\"tf-portfolio-row\">\r\n<div class=\"tf-portfolio-container clearfix\">\r\n\r\n<!-- Start single portfolio -->\r\n<div class=\"col-md-4 col-lg-4 col-sm-6 col-xs-12\">\r\n<div class=\"portfolio\">\r\n<div class=\"portfolio__inner\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section><section class=\"kc-elm kc-css-695212 kc_row#\" data-kc-fullwidth=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"kc-row-container kc-container\">\r\n<div class=\"kc-wrap-columns\">\r\n<div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-402625 kc_col-sm-12 kc_column# kc_col-sm-12\">\r\n<div class=\"kc-col-container\">\r\n<div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-553973 kc_row# kc_row#_inner\">\r\n<div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-257895 kc_col-sm-3 kc_column_inner kc_col-sm-3\">\r\n<div class=\"kc_wrapper kc-col-inner-container\">\r\n<div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-984097 action-button f-right\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>[/kc_column_text][/kc_column][/kc_row]','About Red&FS','','inherit','closed','closed','','1687-revision-v1','','','2018-06-05 18:26:31','2018-06-05 18:26:31','',1687,'http://www.moa-redfs.gov.et/1687-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1