iveness. RED&amp;FS operates within the tenets and framework of the Paris Declaration on Aid Effectiveness.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n<div class=\"grow-img\">\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-medium\" src=\"http://www.moa-redfs.gov.et/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/AboutUs_img1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"720\" height=\"544\" /></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p><!-- humanity & Client Section End --></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"kc-elm kc-css-669716 kc_row#\">\n<div class=\"kc-row-container kc-container\">\n<div class=\"kc-wrap-columns\">\n<div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-773063 kc_col-sm-12 kc_column# kc_col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"kc-col-container\">\n<div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-197423 \">\n<div class=\"section-title section-2 text-center \">\n<h3 style=\"margin: 2rem 0;\"> </h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n[/kc_column_text][vorosa_section_title title=\"UkVEJkZTIE9yZ2FuaXphdGlvbmFsIFN0cnVjdHVyZQ==\" description=\"__empty__\" sec_title_box_icon=\"31\" _id=\"439299\" sec_title_icon_size=\"thumbnail\" custom_css=\"{`kc-css`:{`any`:{`title`:{`font-size|+ .section-title h2`:`30px`}}}}\"][kc_column_text _id=\"782250\"]<div class=\"single-grow mb-20\" style=\"padding: 15px;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 2rem 0;\">RED&amp;FS is built on four pillar Technical Committees (TCs) that mirror the state ministerial structure of the two federal ministries, each chaired by the respective sector state minister and supported by two DP co-chairs. The TCs are: Livestock and Fisheries Production and Marketing; Agriculture Growth; Sustainable Land Management; and Rural Job Opportunity Creation and Food Security. Each TC is further broken down into focused sub-sector Task Forces (TFs) which are chaired by a government director and co-chaired by DP representatives. Oversight to the entire structure is provided through an Executive Committee chaired by the two federal ministers and also supported by DP co-chairs. The platform also features cross-sector TFs not aligned to any specific sector. The RED&amp;FS Secretariat provides broad and agile support to the entire sector and consists of a Government Coordinator, Donor Coordinator, Monitoring and Evaluation (M&amp;E) Expert, and support staff. The RED&amp;FS Organizational Chart is shown below.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"icon-img-2 text-center\" style=\"margin: 2rem 0;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium\" src=\"http://www.moa-redfs.gov.et/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/National-Agricultural-Investment-Framework.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"949\" height=\"695\" /></div>\n[/kc_column_text][/kc_column][/kc_row]','About Us','','inherit','closed','closed','','1687-autosave-v1','','','2018-06-21 17:32:33','2018-06-21 17:32:33','',1687,'http://www.moa-redfs.gov.et/1687-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1715,3,'2018-06-05 19:36:33','2018-06-05 19:36:33','[kc_row use_container=\"yes\" force=\"no\" column_align=\"middle\" video_mute=\"no\" _id=\"239110\"][kc_column width=\"12/12\" _id=\"76761\" css_custom=\"{`kc-css`:{}}\"][kc_column_text css_custom=\"{`kc-css`:{}}\" _id=\"728420\"]<style type=\"text/css\">@media only screen and (min-width: 1000px) and (max-width: 5000px){body.kc-css-system .kc-css-574896{width: 100%;}body.kc-css-system .kc-css-413270{width: 100%;}body.kc-css-system .kc-css-923857{width: 25%;}body.kc-css-system .kc-css-427118{width: 25%;}body.kc-css-system .kc-css-185945{width: 25%;}body.kc-css-system .kc-css-23046{width: 25%;}body.kc-css-system .kc-css-300012{width: 25%;}body.kc-css-system .kc-css-500363{width: 25%;}body.kc-css-system .kc-css-109452{width: 25%;}body.kc-css-system .kc-css-622095{width: 25%;}body.kc-css-system .kc-css-96518{width: 72.5%;}body.kc-css-system .kc-css-257895{width: 27.47%;}}body.kc-css-system .kc-css-958963{padding-top: 120px;padding-bottom: 90px;}body.kc-css-system .kc-css-473629 .section-title{padding-bottom: 50px;}body.kc-css-system .kc-css-433574 .single-grow h3{color: #555555