mage_source=\"media_library\" image=\"1721\"][/kc_column_inner][kc_column_inner width=\"50%\" _id=\"168011\"][kc_row_inner# _id=\"617156\" cols_gap=\"{`kc-css`:{}}\" row_class=\"video-info video-border\" css_custom=\"{`kc-css`:{`479`:{`box`:{`padding|`:`inherit inherit inherit 0px`}},`767`:{`box`:{`padding|`:`inherit inherit inherit 0px`}},`999`:{`box`:{`padding|`:`inherit inherit inherit 0px`}},`any`:{`box`:{`padding|`:`35px inherit inherit 30px`}}}}\"][kc_column_inner# width=\"100%\" _id=\"839579\" css_custom=\"{`kc-css`:{}}\"][kc_title text=\"UHJvZHVjdGl2ZSBTYWZldHkgTmV0IFByb2dyYW0=\" _id=\"17692\" type=\"h3\" css_custom=\"{`kc-css`:{`any`:{`title-style`:{`font-family|+.kc_title,.kc_title,.kc_title a.kc_title_link`:`Roboto Slab`,`font-size|+.kc_title,.kc_title,.kc_title a.kc_title_link`:`30px`}}}}\"][kc_column_text _id=\"781540\" css_custom=\"{`kc-css`:{`any`:{`box`:{`padding|`:`inherit 27px inherit inherit`}}}}\"]\r\n\r\nThe fourth phase Productive Safety Net Program (PSNP 4), spanning from 2015 to 2020, with an investment of 4.8 billion USD, ensures food security through a system of food/cash transfers to vulnerable households. PSNP 4 has the objective to increase access to safety net and disaster risk management systems, complementary livelihoods services, and nutrition support for food insecure households in rural Ethiopia. Three components will contribute to the achievement of the PSNP objective.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>Component one</strong> will provide support to the social protection and disaster risk management systems, including targeting, registration capacity development, management information systems, early warning triggers, and response mechanisms.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Component two</strong> will be delivered through three sub-components delivering key services of:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Safety net transfers to chronically food insecure households and support to a scalable response mechanism for transitory needs;</li>\r\n 	<li>Sustainable community assets and human capital investments and;</li>\r\n 	<li>Enhanced access to complementary livelihoods services for client households through crop and livestock production, off-farm income generating services, and labor/employment linkages.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li>Component three will support sustainable capacity development and institutional strengthening to support the PSNP.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/kc_column_text][/kc_column_inner#][/kc_row_inner#][/kc_column_inner][/kc_row_inner][kc_row_inner _id=\"827605\" cols_gap=\"{`kc-css`:{}}\" css_custom=\"{`kc-css`:{`479`:{`box`:{`margin|`:`30px inherit 30px inherit`}},`any`:{`box`:{`margin|`:`50px inherit 50px inherit`}}}}\"][kc_column_inner width=\"50%\" _id=\"1450\"][kc_row_inner# _id=\"354954\" cols_gap=\"{`kc-css`:{}}\" css_custom=\"{`kc-css`:{`479`:{`box`:{`padding|`:`inherit 0px inherit inherit`}},`767`:{`box`:{`padding|`:`inherit 0px inherit inherit`}},`999`:{`box`:{`padding|`:`inherit 0px inherit inherit`}},`any`:{`typography`:{`text-align|`:`right`},`box`:{`padding|`:`35px 30px inherit inherit`}}}}\" row_class=\"video-info video-border-two\"][kc_column_inner# width=\"100%\" _id=\"148258\" css_custom=\"{`kc-css`:{`any`:{`box`:{`float|`:`right`}}}}\"][kc_title text=\"TmF0aW9uYWwgQWdyaWN1bHR1cmUgSW52ZXN0bWVudCBQbGFuDQoNCg==\" _id=\"627749\" type=\"h3\" css_custom=\"{`kc-css`:{`any`:{`title-style`:{`font-family|+.kc_title,.kc_title,.kc_title a.kc_title_link`:`Roboto Slab`,`font-size|+.kc_title,.kc_title,.kc_title a.kc_title_link`:`30px`,`text-align|+.kc_title,.kc_title,.kc_title a.kc_title_link`:`left`}}}}\"][kc_column_text _id=\"259668\" css_custom=\"{`kc-css`:{`any`:{`typography`:{`text-align|,p`:`left`},`box`:{`padding|`:`inherit inherit inherit 0px`}}}}\"]\r\n\r\nEthiopia’s broad development goals are described in the Growth and Transformation Plan 2 (GTP2) (2015-2020), while agriculture sector goals are defined specifically in the National Agricultural Investment Framework (NAIF), which is currently being develo