roach to capacity building. Nutrition, gender, and climate smart agriculture considerations are mainstreamed throughout all components.</p>\r\n[/kc_column_text][/kc_column_inner#][/kc_row_inner#][/kc_column_inner][/kc_row_inner][kc_row_inner _id=\"402928\" cols_gap=\"{`kc-css`:{}}\" css_custom=\"{`kc-css`:{`479`:{`box`:{`margin|`:`30px inherit 30px inherit`}},`any`:{`box`:{`margin|`:`50px inherit 50px inherit`}}}}\"][kc_column_inner width=\"50%\" _id=\"614701\"][kc_row_inner# _id=\"613365\" cols_gap=\"{`kc-css`:{}}\" css_custom=\"{`kc-css`:{`479`:{`box`:{`padding|`:`inherit 0px inherit inherit`}},`767`:{`box`:{`padding|`:`inherit 0px inherit inherit`}},`999`:{`box`:{`padding|`:`inherit 0px inherit inherit`}},`any`:{`typography`:{`text-align|`:`right`},`box`:{`padding|`:`35px 30px inherit inherit`}}}}\" row_class=\"video-info video-border-two\"][kc_column_inner# width=\"100%\" _id=\"606772\" css_custom=\"{`kc-css`:{`any`:{`box`:{`float|`:`right`}}}}\"][kc_title text=\"U3VzdGFpbmFibGUgTGFuZCBNYW5hZ2VtZW50IFByb2dyYW0NCg==\" _id=\"767369\" type=\"h3\" css_custom=\"{`kc-css`:{`any`:{`title-style`:{`font-family|+.kc_title,.kc_title,.kc_title a.kc_title_link`:`Roboto Slab`,`font-size|+.kc_title,.kc_title,.kc_title a.kc_title_link`:`30px`,`text-align|+.kc_title,.kc_title,.kc_title a.kc_title_link`:`left`,`display|`:`inline-block`}}}}\"][kc_column_text _id=\"525368\" css_custom=\"{`kc-css`:{`any`:{`typography`:{`text-align|,p`:`left`},`box`:{`padding|`:`inherit inherit inherit 0px`}}}}\"]<p>\r\nThe second phase Sustainable Land Management Program (SLMP 2), covering the years 2014-2019 and 107 million USD, conducts activities to rehabilitate and protect natural resources. Its objective is to reduce land degradation and improve land productivity in selected watersheds in the highlands of Ethiopia.</p>\r\n<p>There are four components to the project.</p>\r\n<p>1. Integrated watershed and landscape management supports scale-up and adoption of appropriate sustainable land and wate