=\"animated\">The Rural Economic Development and Food Security (RED&FS) Sector Working Group <span></span></h2>\r\r\n                            <h1 class=\"animated\"> <span></span>  <span></span></h1>\r\r\n                            <p class=\"animated\">Our objective: Facilitate technical, operational and strategic level dialogue between the government and DPs and to mobilize and align development investments towards sector priorities identified by the GoE, as well as to harmonize investment and activities in order to maximize resource effectiveness.</p>\r\r\n\r\r\n							\r\r\n							\r\n\r\r\n							\r\r\n                            <a class=\"button theme-bg animated\" href=\"http://www.moa-redfs.gov.et/about-us/\">LEARN MORE</a>\r\r\n                        </div>\r\r\n                    </div>\r\r\n                </div>\r\r\n				\r\n			\r\r\n				\r\n				<div class=\"single-slider pb-340 pt-240 bg-img\" style=\"background-image:url(http://www.moa-redfs.gov.et/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/24520671422_a45ac55a90_b.jpg);\" data-overlay=\"5\">\r\r\n                    <div class=\"container\">\r\r\n                        <div class=\"slider-text text-center z-index\">\r\r\n                            <h2 class=\"animated\">Working Group <span></span></h2>\r\r\n                            <h1 class=\"animated\"> <span></span>  <span></span></h1>\r\r\n                            <p class=\"animated\">The joint platform brings togehter the Government of Ethiopia (GoE), represented by the federal  Ministry of Agriculture and Natural Resources (MoANR), Ministiry of Livestock and Fisheries (MoLF),  and the main development partners (DPs) engaged in the sectors.</p>\r\r\n\r\r\n							\r\r\n							\r\n\r\r\n							\r\r\n                            <a class=\"button theme-bg animated\" href=\"http://www.moa-redfs.gov.et/faqs\">LEARN MORE</a>\r\r\n                        </div>\r\r\n                    </div>\r\r\n                </div>\r\r\n				\r\n			\r\r\n				\r\n				